I have been obsessed with Mac makeup since my university days in Singapore 20 years ago. I’ve bought all of these shades over the years and have loved them so much. In fact I think their retro matte formula (in shade 3 and 4) is much improved- it used to be quite dry but not anymore. I still recommend conditioning your lips before using them though. 

Kindly ignore the fading Mehindi on my hands - I don’t like this phase of it either. Also the sun’s been playing hide and seek and this was the best light I managed to shoot in. I can’t complain though because while the rest of the country is experiencing a heat wave, some of us in Bangalore are enjoying sweater weather. I hope it isn’t too hot where you are. Stay hydrated and stay well!

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It’s one of her favourite (sad girl aka Olivia Rodrigo) songs. She didn’t want to share this recording with me because she felt like it wasn’t perfect. I think it is beyond perfect. I think it’s pure and real - and that to me surpasses any standard of perfection. She makes me so proud everyday this singing, laughing, quiet,loving, diamond painting girl with the heart and smile so big it lights up my life ✨ ♥️

Special thanks to her music teacher @joshlance7 for letting her love the music she loves and for encouraging her to record her singing.

latestPosts.caption:
Get your Labubu in a day! Here’s how: 

Walk into a @crepdogcrew store in Delhi, Mumbai or Hyderabad- orrrr if you don’t live in these cities, call them on : +919907077077, connect to a store in the city closest to you and have them courier your Labubu to you (courier charges apply of course). If you order via their website you will have to wait 10-15 days.

The other option if you are willing to wait is to order and ship to someone who lives in a country where Pop Mart delivers or have them go buy in the physical store and ship to you or bring back for you if they are coming to India. This is the cheaper option of course. 

You’re welcome ☺️

P.S You can authenticate your Labubu by scanning the QR code on its tag. It takes you to the official Pop Mart authentication site. I just did and they are 💯 authentic! 

P.P.S I said the word ‘cute’ eight times in this reel 😭🫠🙄

Labubu unboxing | Lychee Berry | Green Grape | The Monsters | Macaron

My new ride or die hairbrush by @mantahair 

Hairdresser, entrepreneur, and inventor Tim Binnington created Manta for his wife, Dani, who lost her hair due to a life-threatening illness. As Dani’s hair grew back, Tim watched her comb it with her fingers, too afraid of breakage to use a traditional hairbrush. He created this ultra gentle hairbrush for her so she wouldn’t have to struggle. I find that incredibly romantic. 💕 

This hairbrush is now used and loved by thousands of men and women with all hair types around the world. Because gentle hair brushing is the only way to do it. 

Available on @mynykaa
